        "label": "Once you have entered all of the information for a record, you may progress;\n\n1 - To a new blank record by; keyboard strokes “Control N” or using the button “Create New Record”\n2 - To a new layout or menu by; going to the status area and accessing the oblong under the “Layout” heading; by depressing the blue arrow and clicking on your choice of layout you wish to go to next\n3 - Hide the system from view so you can work on something else; on the main navagation bar at the top of your screen you will see the words “Filemaker Pro”, if you click on this word a drop down menu of actions will appear.  Click on the entry “hide Filemaker Pro” and the screen will disappear into your dock area.",
